title: Rate of premium for the additional F
clause_text: Rate of premium for the additional F.S.I. as mentioned in Column No.3 above shall be 30% for FSI to be used for tenements of size equal to or less than 60 sq.m. and 35% for remaining FSI to be used for residential and / or commercial use, of the rate of the said land mentioned in Annual Statement of Rates without considering the guidelines therein.
